# Bench overlay: console-driven JOG of the LEESN IG28ET stepper drive over RS-485 (CN1).
# MOVES THE MOTOR (FC06 writes). Boots IDLE; the shaft turns only on a typed jog command,
# each bounded to 1-5 s and auto-stopped. Link params from the scan: 115200 8N1, unit 1.
# Use ONLY with the motor mechanically safe (secured, unloaded, current-limited).
# Commands over the USB-Serial-JTAG console: mot-read / mot-enable / mot-disable /
# jog-fwd [s] / jog-rev [s] / jog-stop.
CONFIG_APP_MODBUS_JOG_CONSOLE=y
CONFIG_APP_MODBUS_JOG_UNIT=1
CONFIG_APP_MODBUS_JOG_BAUD=115200
